branchCategory.name: RS
branchCategory.description: <p>Stopper Cylinder series 90-RS is a fixed-height stopper cylinder with proven endurance and low breakaway characteristics&nbsp;is specially designed for use on conveyor lines or other applications requiring an external stopping device.&nbsp;90-RS is made from materials compatible with secondary battery manufacturing. It can be raised or lowered according to the distance required to stop the work piece.&nbsp;</p>
